  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363760/extras/d755dc58b4e601ed91ea623ed54555f2.avif?t=1706611234\" width=608 height=160 /></span><br><br>ReLinked is a pixelated sovietpunk alternate universe game in which the Soviet Union made a breakthrough in science by studying psionic energy. Earth has been invaded by an extraterrestrial civilization and is defended by psionics - people with supernatural abilities. You will have to beat off waves of enemies and think through tactics to fight back.<br><br>Game Features:<br>- 30 skills;<br>- 12 types of weapons, both melee and ranged;<br>- construction;<br>- bossed;<br>- and waves of enemies!",
